channeldata.description: Core Library for Google Client Libraries -------------------------  This package does not include the grpc, grpcio-gcp or grpcgcp extra requirements.  This library is not meant to stand-alone. Instead it defines common helpers used by all Google API clients. For more information, see the [documentation](https://googleapis.dev/python/google-api-core/latest/index.html).  Supported Python Versions ------------------------- Python >= 3.5  Deprecated Python Versions -------------------------- Python == 2.7 - Python 2.7 support will be removed on January 1, 2020. - protobuf does not support Visual C++ 2008, windows py27 package not available
